    "Spells: Permeability (pass through walls/doors), Firefly (light), Dizzy Dean (disorient enemies), Methuselah (age/time), Unravel (undo things), Bliss, Lycanthropy. Cast with CAST or AT [target].",
    "Stars: 13 stars hidden throughout the castle must be collected and dropped in the hollow tree (room 19).",
    "Permeability spell: Essential for passing through locked oak doors and potentially walls.",
    "Fire bricks: Protect from lava when crossing the stream in the underground caverns.",
    "Secret walls: In the plain room (10), PUSH/PULL walls in different directions to reveal hidden rooms.",
    "Swimming: Use SWIM with specific directions (SWIM DOWN, SWIM UP, etc.). Undirected swimming in enchanted water kills you.",
    "Do NOT SAY anything underwater - instant drowning.",
    "Drawbridge lever: In the entryway (room 28), use the lever to lower the drawbridge for permanent castle access.",
    "The fountain system connects the courtyard fountain to the kitchen drain via underwater passages.",
    "Broken glass: Found on the chandelier, useful as a cutting tool.",
    "Potions: Found in the loft, provide magical abilities when drunk."
